pl.coderslab.entity

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.coderslab.entity.User

  • @Entity
public class User
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity representing data stored in table users in the bet24 database. Also used by Hibernate to build database and sql relations. This entity represents a user (client) but at the same time is used by Spring Security together with Role entity
